name: Senka Noble - Liu Xuan
desc:
Your opponent cannot target this card for an attack while you control another "Senka" monster. You can only use each of these effects of "Senka Noble - Liu Xuan" once per turn.
● If you control fewer monsters than your opponent: You can send 1 card you control or in your hand to the GY; Special Summon 1 "Senka" monster from your Deck, except "Senka Noble - Liu Xuan".
● If an attack is declared for a battle involving another “Senka” monster you control: You can draw one card.
